<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Check-in Reminder</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Check-in Reminder</h1>
    <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that your check-in is tomorrow:</p>
    
    <h2>Booking Details</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Property: {{propertyName}}</li>
        <li>Room: {{roomName}}</li>
        <li>Address: {{propertyAddress}}</li>
        <li>Check-in Date: {{startDate}}</li>
        <li>Check-out Date: {{endDate}}</li>
        <li>Check-in Time: {{checkInTime}}</li>
        <li>Check-out Time: {{checkOutTime}}</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Please remember to bring a valid ID and your booking confirmation.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at: {{contactInfo}}</p>
    
    <p>We look forward to welcoming you!</p>
</body>
</html>